Music superstar, Justin Beiber, has announced that his health is deteriorating. The 28-year-old made a three-minute video on Friday to share his condition with the public. Beiber said he’s suffering facial paralysis and needed to take a long rest. “As you can probably see with my face. I have this syndrome called Ramsay Hunt syndrome.” Beiber explained that the cause is a virus that attacks the nerves in his ear, facial nerves “and has caused my face to have paralysis”. “I’ve done everything to get better but my sickness is getting worse”, he said, The Canadian singer earlier announced that he was postponing a few shows of his Justice World Tour due to “non-Covid related illness”.